                    <span>I think this is a must read book. Easy to read and entertaining. I really believe that at some point in our lives we all fall into one or more of the temptations. It is almost impossible to avoid them, mostly because we are unable to identify them. This book really opened my eyes and it will certainly open yours too.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">widely applicable</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
